britain to mint new `` britannia '' gold coin britain will from next autumn mint and market a new bullion coin call the `` britannia '' contain one ounc of 24 carat gold , togeth with bullion coin of smaller denomin , a treasuri offici said . the new invest coin , to be sold worldwid , will fluctuat in price accord to the intern price of gold . the smaller coin will be in denomin of a half ounc , a quarter ounc and a tenth of an ounc . reuter